title: Waves of Malolo, Fiji
description:
Welcome to episode 74 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today's episode features the relaxing waves of Malolo, Fiji. This episode includes sounds of calm waves, and occasional footsteps walking on sand. There is no whispering. Enjoy!

Visit our website: www.SleepandRelaxASMR.com to get updates and access to special promos on awesome brands!
